方法参数类，扩展参数可以继承Parameters自己实现
参考：
<pre>
{
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
        "location": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "The city and state, e.g. San Francisco, CA"
        },
        "unit": {"type": "string", "enum": ["celsius", "fahrenheit"]}
    },
    "required": ["location"]
}
</pre>

